data.description:
Welcome to your ideal investment opportunity! Nestled on a serene and quiet street, this charming duplex offers a lucrative income stream with tenants currently paying a total of $1900 a month in rent. Rest easy knowing that the tenants are up to date with their payments, providing you with a stable and reliable rental income.

The left side apartment has undergone a recent remodel, with recent paint and upgrades to the kitchen and bathroom.  Both apartments include hardwood flooring.  In addition to the interior upgrades, the duplex boasts separated back yards, providing privacy and individual outdoor spaces for each unit. 

Convenience is key, and this duplex offers just that with its short commute to Fort Drum. Whether your tenants are military personnel or individuals working in the area, the location is sure to be a significant selling point. The proximity to Fort Drum adds a layer of desirability, making this property an excellent investment.

Don't miss out on this fantastic real estate opportunity. Schedule a viewing today and envision the potential of this well-maintained and income-generating duplex!
